Title : Odd Henrik Sælen
Text : {{Orphan|date=June 2016}}

'''Odd Henrik Sælen''' (8 June 1920 – 23 January 2008) is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] oceanographer.

He was born in [[Bergen]]. He took the [[dr.philos.]] degree in 1963, became a professor of physical oceanography at the [[University of Oslo]] in 1965 and a fellow of the [[Norwegian Academy of Science and Letters]] in 1971. From 1978 to his retirement he served at the [[University of Bergen]].<ref name=snl>{{cite encyclopedia|year=|title=Odd Henrik Sælen|encyclopedia=[[Store norske leksikon]]|editor=|publisher=|location=|url=http://snl.no/Odd_Henrik_S%C3%A6len|language=Norwegian|accessdate=4 May 2014}}</ref>

